<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你不是说要在森林里活下去 必须有什么吃什么吗</font>

303
00:20:08,358 --> 00:20:12,598
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我确实这么说过 但这实在是…</font>

304
00:20:15,838 --> 00:20:16,808
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">很好吃</font>

305
00:20:17,898 --> 00:20:21,128
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真怀念啊 这是卤煮大蝗虫吧</font>

306
00:20:21,398 --> 00:20:22,228
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">卤煮？</font>

307
00:20:22,778 --> 00:20:24,268
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是卤煮吗</font>

308
00:20:24,928 --> 00:20:29,028
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是的 主要是用酱水和白糖调位</font>

309
00:20:29,478 --> 00:20:30,688
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">酱水？</font>

310
00:20:31,128 --> 00:20:36,058
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">酱水是妖狼族喜爱的一种调味料</font>

311
00:20:37,408 --> 00:20:40,988
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">妖狼族会将豆子用盐腌制后使其发酵</font>

312
00:20:41,178 --> 00:20:43,998
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">做成一直叫豆酱的调味料</font>

313
00:20:44,378 --> 00:20:49,068
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而在制作过程中将上层液体单独拿出来发酵</font>

314
00:20:49,218 --> 00:20:50,618
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">最后做出来的就是酱水了</font>

315
00:20:51,388 --> 00:20:56,108
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">两种都是这个国家没有的独特调味料 嗯</font>

316
00:20:56,558 --> 00:21:01,508
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说穿了 豆酱就是味噌 酱水就是酱油</font>

317
00:21:03,688 --> 00:21:05,828
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">相马 你打算吃吗</font>

318
00:21:17,998 --> 00:21:19,358
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">相马你这是哭了？</font>

319
00:21:19,738 --> 00:21:25,318
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这怎么忍得住 这可是我故乡的味道</font>

320
00:21:25,948 --> 00:21:27,638
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">相马故乡的味道</font>

321
00:21:29,518 --> 00:21:33,248
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">令人怀念的味道越嚼越足</font>

322
00:21:33,838 --> 00:21:36,808
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个世界有酱油 有味噌</font>

323
00:21:37,488 --> 00:21:41,488
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">想要品尝那些熟悉的味道不再是梦想了</font>

324
00:21:44,668 --> 00:21:48,948
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个 陛下 不好意思在您感动的时候打扰您</font>

325
00:21:49,258 --> 00:21:51,558
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们该介绍下一份食材了</font>

326
00:21:55,188 --> 00:21:58,058
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 抱歉 你们继续吧</font>

327
00:21:58,748 --> 00:22:01,188
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么邦乔先生 请上下一种食材</font>

328
00:22:02,408 --> 00:22:04,958
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是它</font>

329
00:22:09,988 --> 00:22:13,938
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风 穿越整个世界</font>

330
00:22:14,168 --> 00:22:18,288
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">连接不可能相遇的我们</font>

331
00:22:18,388 --> 00:22:22,418
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">展开没有人看得见的羽翼</font>

332
00:22:22,598 --> 00:22:26,528
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">找寻没有人看得见的奇迹</font>

333
00:22:26,528 --> 00:22:29,838
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">起飞吧</font>

334
00:22:35,428 --> 00:22:39,568
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">继续迷惘明日的方向</font>

335
00:22:39,618 --> 00:22:43,718
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">追求继续选择的勇气</font>

336
00:22:43,858 --> 00:22:47,928
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不曾怀疑天空有多蓝</font>

337
00:22:47,988 --> 00:22:52,388
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望我能毫不畏惧世事无常</font>

338
00:22:52,588 --> 00:22:54,808
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起将来的梦想</font>

339
00:22:54,808 --> 00:22:56,898
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">超越想象中的未来</font>

340
00:22:56,898 --> 00:23:00,958
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这般时光是如此美好</font>

341
00:23:01,198 --> 00:23:03,258
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只想徜徉在其中</font>

342
00:23:03,378 --> 00:23:05,428
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和你共同度过现在</font>

343
00:23:05,428 --> 00:23:08,798
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要是能实现就好了</font>

344
00:23:08,798 --> 00:23:13,588
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">穿过湛蓝 绵延不断的天空</font>

345
00:23:13,738 --> 00:23:17,428
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将轮回的命运拉近身边</font>

346
00:23:17,428 --> 00:23:21,848
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">传达思念给紧握的手</font>

347
00:23:21,848 --> 00:23:26,588
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">仅仅希望这就是永远</font>

348
00:23:26,648 --> 00:23:28,638
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使现在只是幻影</font>

349
00:23:28,838 --> 00:23:31,028
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算是在某人的梦境里</font>

350
00:23:31,028 --> 00:23:32,758
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风</font>

351
00:23:32,758 --> 00:23:37,598
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在抓住它 起飞吧</font>

